reviews.review_text: I was there Gosh how nice to hear this Dead show once again.  It was the only ticket I ever bought to go see them, altho my friends and I all goofed around in the parkinglot from Fri-Sun as all did back then.  Hearing their last song "Touch of Grey" again, EXACTLY as it was, is amazing!!!  THANK YOU so much for this recording.  Jerry's 70th birthday was earlier in the week and the anniversary of his death in a few days and it has me reminiscing some fun times back before settling down/getting a real job/married/having kids.  Love this!!!
